{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::d105d6a0-821c-11ee-a556-57faa9bf16e4","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nEmbark on an extraordinary charter experience aboard the Lagoon 46 “Moondance.” This luxurious catamaran offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and indulgence. With an obligatory skipper to navigate the waters and the option to have a hostess cater to your every need, “Moondance” guarantees an unforgettable sailing adventure.\n\nThe Lagoon 46 “Moondance” features four spacious cabins and four toilets, ensuring privacy and convenience for all guests. Each cabin is meticulously designed to provide a comfortable retreat, allowing you to unwind and rejuvenate after a day of exploration.\n\nWith an obligatory skipper at the helm, you can sit back, relax, and fully immerse yourself in the joy of sailing. The skipper’s expertise and knowledge of the local waters will ensure a safe and smooth voyage, allowing you to focus on creating lifelong memories.\n\nTo elevate your charter experience even further, “Moondance” offers the option to have a hostess on board. The hostess will take care of your culinary needs, providing delightful meals and refreshing beverages throughout your journey. Their presence adds an extra layer of luxury and convenience, allowing you to truly indulge in the pleasures of the sea.\n\nWhether you’re seeking adventure, relaxation, or a combination of both, the Lagoon 46 “Moondance” promises to exceed your expectations. From the moment you step on board, you’ll be greeted by a world of elegance and sophistication. So sit back, enjoy the breathtaking views, and let “Moondance” whisk you away on a charter experience like no other.","blueprint":{"name":"MOONDANCE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d105d6a0-821c-11ee-a556-57faa9bf16e4::assets::de54b2d0-412a-11f0-859e-7f35bbe14603/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d105d6a0-821c-11ee-a556-57faa9bf16e4::assets::de6